  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our community</h1><p></p><br><h1>Also recommended for you</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479220/extras/7ad5a827cc23b585b58d96652c32df7e.poster.avif?t=1705613450\" width=528 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479220/extras/7ad5a827cc23b585b58d96652c32df7e.webm?t=1705613450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479220/extras/7ad5a827cc23b585b58d96652c32df7e.mp4?t=1705613450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Embark on a journey deep into the forest, in medieval times, in search of a princess locked away in a castle. Unravel puzzles based on the classic game Peg Solitaire, which will challenge you on this journey in search of the princess. Find your way to solve each challenge that will lead you closer to the red castle. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479220/extras/9a49f54f2aeadcb15b1312b4a80b71e1.poster.avif?t=1705613450\" width=450 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479220/extras/9a49f54f2aeadcb15b1312b4a80b71e1.webm?t=1705613450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479220/extras/9a49f54f2aeadcb15b1312b4a80b71e1.mp4?t=1705613450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🧭 Explore enchanting locations such as forests, ancient ruins and picturesque villages, each of which holds riddles to be deciphered.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🏞Dazzle 12 landscapes, lovingly crafted and full of details.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"